latestPosts.caption:
My Nanu’s always been a very curious person, someone who till date will never be without his personal holy trifecta - a book, a pen, and a notebook. 📔 

You will find him reading about life, history, politics, religion, and fiction. Truly anything the literary world has to offer, my Nanu has read it. 
He’s the smartest, kindest, and cutest person I know. 💕

So this Father’s Day along with FNP’s wide range of gifts, I decided to add to his collection of pens and notebooks that I know for sure, he’ll love and use. 🌟

Thanks to @fernsnpetalsindia for helping me have this absolutely wholesome moment with my Nanu. He was so excited about the pens and the customisation offered with his name on the gifts. 🖊️ 📔

Happy Father’s Day! 🌸

#FNP #Gift #FathersDay
